      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>When developing educational material for your online\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tbanking customers, it’s important to keep in mind both the\r\n");
