      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tinformation security jargon.</p>\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>The following sections outline common security tips that\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tcould be included in your bank’s online banking customer\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\teducation material. The tips provided below are not exhaustive,\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tbut they should provide a good starting point.</p>\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 style=\"color: green;\">General PC Security</h2>\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul>\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li><strong>Update your software frequently</strong> to\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tensure you have the latest security patches. This includes\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tyour computer’s operating system and other installed software\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t(e.g. Web Browsers, Adobe Flash Player, Adobe Reader, Java,\r\n");
