      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li><strong>Use a cable lock to physically secure\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tlaptops</strong> when these devices are stored in an untrusted\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tlocation.</li>\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</ul>\r\n");
      out.write("\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 style=\"color: green;\">General Online Security</h2>\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul>\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li><strong>Never click on suspicious links</strong> in\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\temails, tweets, posts, or online advertising. Links can take\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tyou to a different website than their labels indicate. Typing\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tan address in your browser instead of clicking a link in an\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\temail is a safer alternative.</li>\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li><strong>Only give sensitive information to\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\twebsites using encryption</strong> so your information is protected as\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tit travels across the Internet. Verify the web address begins\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\twith “https://” (the “s” is for secure) rather than just\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t“http://.” Some browsers also display a closed padlock.</li>\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li><strong>Do not trust sites with certificate\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\twarnings or errors.</strong> These messages could be caused by your\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tconnection being intercepted or the web server misrepresenting\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tits identity.</li>\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li><strong>Avoid using public computers or\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tpublic wireless access points</strong> for online banking and other\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tactivities involving sensitive information when possible.</li>\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li><strong>Always “sign out” or “log off”</strong> of\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tpassword protected websites when finished to prevent\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tunauthorized access. Simply closing the browser window may not\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tactually end your session.</li>\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li><strong>Be cautious of unsolicited phone\r\n");
