      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\trequesting sensitive information.</li>\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</ul>\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 style=\"color: green;\">Password Best Practices</h2>\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul>\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li><strong>Create a unique password for all the\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tdifferent systems you use.</strong> If you don’t, then one breach\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tleaves all your accounts vulnerable.</li>\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li><strong>Never share your password over the\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tphone, in texts, by email, or in person.</strong> If you are asked for\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tyour password, it’s probably a scam.</li>\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li><strong>Use unpredictable passwords</strong> with a\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tcombination of lowercase letters, capital letters, numbers,\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tand special characters.</li>\r\n");
      out.write("\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li><strong>The longer the password, the tougher\r\n");
